Backend (Node.js + Express)
├── Auth (JWT) — Customer / Agent / Admin roles
├── Zone & Rate Card management (admin)
├── Order creation + Rate calculation engine
├── Auto-assignment logic (nearest agent by zone)
├── Status lifecycle + immutable tracking log
├── Failed delivery + reschedule flow
└── Email notifications (Nodemailer + Gmail/SendGrid free tier)

Frontend (React + Vite)
├── Customer: Register, Login, Place Order, Track Order
├── Agent: View assigned orders, Update status
└── Admin: Manage zones, rate cards, orders, agents, override status

Database: PostgreSQL (via Prisma ORM)
Deploy: Railway (backend + DB) + Vercel (frontend)
